nodes.title: Update the maven conf to build an OSGi bundle
Ensure that no SecureDirectoryStream operations will throw NPE when the directory the SDS references has been deleted.
Bump actions/cache from v2.1.4 to v2.1.5
Bump actions/setup-java from v1 to v2
Remove attempt to skip CI for the force-push to a PR just before merge.
Explicitly wrap if condition with operator in `${{ }}`.
Add CI step to cancel previous runs (for the same branch) that are still running when starting a new run.
Attempt to avoid running CI tests for the commit that gets force pushed to a PR just before it is merged.
Remove Travis config and switch build status badge to use GitHub Actions.
Switch Javadoc/JDiff generation from JDK 15 to 11, since it seems like the doclet API that JDiff is built on was [removed in JDK 13](https://bugs.java.com/bugdatabase/view_bug.do?bug_id=8215584).
Set batch mode for CI Maven builds. This should suppress some output that isn't useful like download progress.
Bump actions/cache from v2 to v2.1.4
Don't try to test on JDK 7; building requires JDK 8.
First pass at github actions CI for Jimfs.
Update Jimfs README to refer to 1.2.
Remove stray letter and fix indentation.
Adding ppc64le architecture support on travis-ci
Add travis config for guava-beta-checker and fix deploy_snapshot.sh for jimfs to actually work with the JDKs we're building with on travis.
`Files.newOutputStream(path, CREATE, TRUNCATE_EXISTING)` does not truncate the existing file
Modifier 'private' is redundant for enum constructors.
Fix the outdated link of google's java style guide
Fix exception message - add missing closing parenthesis
Removed TODO comment for making heap disks configurable, as its alrea…
Throw UOE when setting unsupported attributes
No need to disable doclint completely
